item.title: Level 20 wildy teleport *PLEASE HELP*
item.dc:creator: @i0wn3v3ry i0wn3v3ry
item.description:
@i0wn3v3ry wrote:

ajisamazing:

Try going to config.java and search “NO_TELEPORT_WILD_LEVEL” or whatever it is in your source and change whatever the number says. For example if the number says WILD_LEVEL = 0 change the 0 to 20. This may only work with some sources. Hope I helped.

I think that is PI only, not sure.
